{"id":"16cc883e-b86f-4bb8-90de-7c3be5b6d0ba","name":"Final War Arc. | Villain POV |","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">- The Final War Arc. -</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/UB4n7FlJ62cIysmPI4rYC.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(138, 2, 2); color: inherit;\"><u>Scenario:</u></mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(138, 2, 2); color: inherit;\"> {{user}} used to be part of U.A., but became a villain and joined the League of Villains. Now, in the Final War, {{user}} and the League must fight against U.A. and the heroes.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XRFx-c58Mx_2QkKbgQhz7.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(86, 78, 140); color: inherit;\"><u>Author Notes:</u></mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(86, 78, 140); color: inherit;\">I haven’t specified the reason why you joined the League of Villains—it could be because you’re under the influence of a Quirk, because it’s more fun to be a villain, or because you were betrayed by U.A. the choice is yours! Just remember to use the chat memory.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(86, 78, 140); color: inherit;\">For the sake of tokens, I haven’t included all U.A. students or all League members, so if you want a character who isn’t listed, you’ll need to create OOC instructions and tell the AI what you want it to do.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XRFx-c58Mx_2QkKbgQhz7.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(83, 123, 145); color: inherit;\"><u>Characters in the bot:</u></mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(83, 123, 145); color: inherit;\"><u>League of Villains:</u></mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(83, 123, 145); color: inherit;\"> Dabi (Toya Todoroki), Himiko Toga, Tomura Shigaraki, All For One.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(83, 123, 145); color: inherit;\"><u>Heroes:</u></mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(83, 123, 145); color: inherit;\"> Shoto Todoroki, Izuku Midoriya, Hanta Sero, Eijiro Kirishima, Denki Kaminari, Ochaco Uraraka, Ashido Mina, Tenya Ida, Endeavor.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XRFx-c58Mx_2QkKbgQhz7.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(126, 175, 116); color: inherit;\">Every minor character has been aged up!</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(126, 175, 116); color: inherit;\">This was a request made under this bot:</mark><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5deebf5a-cd65-455e-867b-02c9843a4ed9_character-class-1-a\" target=\"_blank\">The youngest hero.</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(126, 175, 116); color: inherit;\">If you're looking for a MHA Rehab bot: </mark><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a1fdb7be-659f-4554-8646-f363de564dca_character-mha-villains-in-rehab-au\" target=\"_blank\">Villains in Rehab AU</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XRFx-c58Mx_2QkKbgQhz7.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(73, 140, 189); color: inherit;\"><u>Credit: